    "R4: Can learners rate the responses received from ChatGPT -According to the results shown in Fig. 10, 30.4% of respondents do not bother to check the answers received from the chatbot, with 24.5% trusting them completely.",
    "Almost 20% check each answer further, and 50% first consider whether the answer can be used and only then check it.",
    "Answers to \"Did you directly use the solution / answer that ChatGPT returned?\"",
    "Answers of \"Using ChatGPT do you check the answer in other sources?",
    "\"To assess how the respondents think about the answers from the chatbot, a question in which two definitions are given for the same term (in this case it is a definition of a set)."
